main event: A round silver white object was observed through radar at Rockport AFS, Texas on 9 January 1963.
interesting points: The object was detected at a distance of about 30 miles., The sighting occurred during daylight and lasted from 8:30 to 8:35 pm CST., The object followed a straight flight path., It appeared briefly on radar before disappearing., The observation was made by an unknown civilian using binoculars.
